e freedom of scientific investigation and international cooperation to this end; prohibited take all the measures of a military nature in the Antarctic, freeze States Antarctic territorial claims of the 12 countries entitled to participate in the consultative meeting is the Consultative Parties to the Antarctic Treaty, and later joined the country to join the country. treaty provisions, the acceding countries in the Antarctic establish a scientific research station or the dispatch of a scientific expedition to carry out research activities, which have expressed interest in the Antarctic, the right to become the Consultative Parties. since June 23, 1961, since the entry into force of the Antarctic Treaty consultative meeting held every two years, by Consultative Parties take turns to host the meeting in addition to the exchange of intelligence, consultation, also expounded consider and the Consultative Parties government recommended measures aimed at promoting the principles and purposes of the treaty. (lssdjt.cn) <br> \"Antarctic Treaty\" gradually improve the system as the situation continues to change and enrich the 1972 and 1980 under the initiative of the Consultative Parties, has negotiation of the Convention for the Conservation of Antarctic Seals, the Convention on the Conservation of Antarctic Marine Living Resources. <br>'
